title: Cheslie Kryst, Former Miss USA, Dies at 30 After Falling From NYC Apartment Building
sub_head: Police are investigating the death of the former civil litigation attorney and entertainment correspondent as a possible suicide
body:
Police are investigating the death of Cheslie Kryst, a former Miss USA who died after falling from a New York City high-rise building, as a possible suicide.
Officers were called to the Orion condo building in Midtown Manhattan just after 7 a.m. ET Sunday where Ms. Kryst was found dead at the scene, a spokesman for the New York Police Department said.
